Name: Pinball Lockdown
About the game: Play Pinball Lockdown! A unique exciting collection of pinball tables with a variety of themes. No hidden extras, 5 tables available from day one. Discover thrilling tables with challenges and missions, including dragons, outer space, casinos, and wonderland. Featuring a table based on Onteca’s hit retro game Space Ribbon and a classic Alice in Wonderland Table with original illustrations. Tables: . Las Vegas . Alice’s Adventures in Wonderland . Dragon Land . Space Ribbon . Zen Garden
